Rental & Parties
Interested in renting our beautiful, state-of-the-art 203 seat theatre, gorgeous lobby or multiple dance/banquet rooms?  Call us at
772.283.2313
or email us at
info@starstruckfl.org
today to setup a tour and discuss your needs!
PARTIES
CELEBRATE YOUR BIRTHDAY AT STARSTRUCK!
Love Broadway Shows? FROZEN, Pirates or Princesses?  How about Disco or Hip-Hop? The theme options are limitless for a StarStruck Party! StarStruck's entertaining and professional staff will teach you and your guests an entire song with complete choreography from a show or a theme of your choice! Get excited to sing & dance to musicals like
GREASE, THE WIZARD OF OZ, ANNIE,
and
HIGH SCHOOL MUSICAL
or to the music of pop stars like
JUSTIN BIEBER, TAYLOR SWIFT
or
ARIANA GRANDE!
Birthday guests are encouraged to arrive in costume for the full theme party experience (for example: Annie is the birthday girl and her guests arrive as orphans, OR Danny Zuko is the birthday boy and his guests arrive as T-Birds & Pink Ladies). StarStruck Birthdays are not just for the little ones! Have a 40th coming up? Call Now!
Please call StarStruck at 772.283.2313 for reservations and availability.
